  "subject": "Fix remote debugger address property",
  "commit_message": "Fix remote debugger address property\n\nBefore Java 11 to attach a remote debugger, we could specify JVM arguments such as this:\n-agentlib:jdwp=transport=dt_socket,address=8787,server=y,suspend=n\nHowever, this does not allow connecting to the VM with a remote debugger.\nTo allow this, we need to slightly adjust the address property to be this:\n-agentlib:jdwp=transport=dt_socket,address=*:8787,server=y,suspend=n\n\nIssue-ID: SDC-3288\nSigned-off-by: aribeiro <anderson.ribeiro@est.tech>\nChange-Id: I01b824be7cee2c371f2b09a629e68e5d6e44a055\n",
